parameters.name: Ip
parameters.description: The IP address of the BE cluster.

parameters.name: NetworkType
parameters.description:
The network type.

Valid value:

*   Tenant: Tenant.
*   VPC

parameters.name: PageNumber
parameters.description: The page number of the page to return. Pages start from page 1. Default value: 1.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries to return on each page. Default value: 20.

parameters.name: ResourceGroupId
parameters.description: The ID of the resource group.

parameters.name: Status
parameters.description:
The status of the enterprise-level snapshot policy.

Valid value:

*   Create Failed: the creation failure.
*   Delete Failed: the that failed to be deleted.
*   Executing
*   Available: The template is available.
*   Deleting

parameters.name: Type
parameters.description:
The type of the variable.

Valid value:

*   CUSTOM: custom type.
*   DEFAULT: system type.

parameters.name: VpcId
parameters.description: The ID of the virtual private cloud (VPC).
